cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with automated surface segmentation in medical images using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) domains. The use of Conditional Random Fields (CRFs) also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The application of the proposed model on medical datasets further indicates the involvement of multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
